OL,3,CLabour blame game begins as Plaid
OL,4,CCymru poised to lead Wales
OL,6,FOne Labour MP told me the party needed
OL,7,Fto show "humility" and accept voters
OL,8,Fwere angry about issues much closer to
OL,9,Fhome: struggling public services, the
OL,10,Fdeeply unpopular default 20mph policy,
OL,11,Fand questions around political
OL,12,Fdonations.
OL,14,FOthers argue these problems pre-date
OL,15,FKeir Starmer's arrival in Downing
OL,16,FStreet. Polling had shown Labour
OL,17,Fsupport in Wales weakening well before
OL,18,Fthe general election.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
