OL,3,CLabour blame game begins as Plaid
OL,4,CCymru poised to lead Wales
OL,6,FOne MP put it bluntly: "The rot set in
OL,7,Funder Mark Drakeford. This has been on
OL,8,Fthe cards for years."
OL,10,FFor Plaid Cymru, there is jubilation
OL,11,Fat an historic breakthrough, but also
OL,12,Fcaution. Senior figures know that many
OL,13,Fvoters may have backed the party
OL,14,Ftactically to stop Reform UK.
OL,16,FOne Plaid MS told me this morning they
OL,17,Fwere "acutely aware" of that reality
OL,18,Fand that the party would now need to
OL,19,Fwork hard to keep that support.
OL,26,@nD@XOUpD@UO]yD@FOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
