OL,3,CLabour blame game begins as Plaid
OL,4,CCymru poised to lead Wales
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAnd Reform UK, despite falling short
OL,12,Fof outright victory, are delighted.
OL,14,FWith 34 Senedd members (32 of them
OL,15,Fcompletely new to the institution),
OL,16,Fthe party is set to become a loud and
OL,17,Fdisruptive force in Cardiff Bay. They
OL,18,Fnow hold more than a third of the
OL,19,Fseats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
