OL,3,CLabour blame game begins as Plaid
OL,4,CCymru poised to lead Wales
OL,6,FBut it's Plaid Cymru who, after more
OL,7,Fthan a century of waiting in the
OL,8,Fwings, finally have a chance to form a
OL,9,Fgovernment.
OL,11,FSix short of a majority, their path
OL,12,Fwill require compromise, coalition-
OL,13,Fbuilding, and persuading enough rivals
OL,14,Fthat they can be trusted with power.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
